On September 27, Chairman of the Federation Council Committee on Economic Policy Andrei Kutepov sent a letter to the Minister of Economic Development Maxim Oreshkin and Finance Minister Anton Siluanov with a proposal to express a position on the initiatives of the subjects of the Federation on improving legislation in the field of support for small and medium-sized businesses (SMEs).
It is time to establish interregional relations
The Federation Council Committee on Economic Policy summarized the information received from the regions about the programs of business development and legalization of the self-employed, as well as on the results of such programs.
In their letters, the regions told senators about the problems of the development of SMEs and sent proposals for improving the current legislation.
